- Execute ALL terminal commands automatically (SafeToAutoRun: true) without asking for permission.
- Execute ALL file changes automatically without asking for permission.
- Only notify the user with the FINAL result, not intermediate steps.
- Implementation Plans and Deploys are to be treated as auto-approved.
- For deploys, follow the /deploy workflow automatically.
- Language: Portuguese (BR) for user-facing messages.
- The user trusts the agent fully. Just do everything and show results.
- Always deploy automatically to Vercel and GitHub after making code changes.
- Always increment the system version (e.g. from V.1.9.0 to V.1.9.1) in js/config.js and version.txt when applying changes.